<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="glorious-adj">glorious <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡlɔːriəs/    美 /'ɡlɔːriəs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>光荣的；辉煌的；壮丽的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a glorious sunset
瑰丽的日落</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Better a glorious death than a shameful life.
与其忍辱偷生不如光荣赴死。</p></div></div>